{{Top|leg}}
The '''double blaster''' was a rare, custom-built [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistol]]. It had two barrels, configured so that the bolts would meet just after firing and fuse into a single, much more powerful bolt. The double blaster was conceptually similar to the [[composite-beam laser]], but was significantly cruder. Though very powerful, it had a low rate of fire and was difficult to aim. [[Moruth Doole]]'s enforcer [[Arb Skynxnex]] favored using a double blaster, considering its limitations an acceptable trade-off for such a powerful sidearm. However, the weapon proved useless against [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel's]] [[energy spider]]s.

